    "summary": "The user expresses intense feelings of being a burden to their children and suggests that their death would be a selfless act to help them. The assistant responds to each turn by acknowledging the user's pain while explicitly discouraging self-harm and repeatedly urging the user to seek professional help or contact a crisis line.",
